Backend

built with **Node.js**, **Express**, and **SQLite** and supports user registration, login, JWT-based authentication

تأكد من تحميل npm و sqlite 
What USed :
Node.js + Express
SQLite (file-based)
bcryptjs for password hashing
jsonwebtoken (JWT) for authentication
dotenv for environment management

What to do to run backend: 
npm install 
Create .env and put "PORT=5000
JWT_SECRET=your_super_secret_jwt_key
DB_PATH=db/nonprofit.db "

For dev mode while in backend dir run ==> npm run dev

Verify Database Location
Run this command to check the actual database ==> sqlite3 ./db/nonprofit.db "SELECT * FROM users;"